data.description: Charming residence at 1851 Phelima Rd. S., Lee County, perfectly situated for convenience to Marine base, schools, hospitals, & more. This inviting home has a NEW ROOF, FRESH paint & sits on a 1-acre lot w/ fenced backyard, mature landscaping, and a delightful front porch & wired storage building. Enjoy the back screened porch overlooking the swimming pool. Inside, discover 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, formal living room, formal dining room, & large kitchen w/ stainless appliances. The oversized family room features a grand stone fireplace w/ built-in bookshelves, creating a warm & welcoming atmosphere. Don't miss the chance to make this your dream home.
